snippet: Milos Raonic dedicated his third-round win over Viktor Troicki at the Australian Open on Saturday to victims of the school shooting that rocked the remote Canadian town of La Loche....
lead_paragraph: Milos Raonic dedicated his third-round win over Viktor Troicki at the Australian Open on Saturday to victims of the school shooting that rocked the remote Canadian town of La Loche.

headline.print_headline: Raonic Dedicates Win to La Loche Victims
headline.main: Raonic Dedicates Win to La Loche Victims
